// AI-UI Component Type Catalog
// Defines the 22 UI components used by the AI-powered render_ui system,
// grouped into five categories: input, data display, interactive, layout,
// and mermaid integration. Also exports a catalog constant and a runtime
// validation helper.

Components are composable: Wizard, Tabs, Accordion, Card, Section, and
Columns can nest other UIComponent instances as children or step content.
The COMPONENT_CATALOG constant lists all component names by category.
ALL_COMPONENTS is a flat array derived from the catalog.

FUNCTION isValidComponentType(type) -> boolean                             EXPORT
  Check whether the given string appears in the ALL_COMPONENTS array.
  Return true if it is a known component type, false otherwise.
